    "questionText": "A movie was screened for 3 days – Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday. The respective ratio between the number of spectators on Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday was $2:3:5$ and the price charged for three days was in the respective ratio $2:3:4$. If the difference between the amount earned on Tuesday and Wednesday was Rs. 8800, what was the total amount earned in all three days?",
